The paper discusses a tool for automatically generating Python bindings for C++ libraries, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL) categories. The use of LLVM/Clang technologies and the Mako templating engine suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL) applications.
